sagex.phoenix.metadata.proxy

Class AbstractMetadataProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • sagex.phoenix.metadata.proxy.AbstractMetadataProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.reflect.InvocationHandler, ISageMetadata, IPropertyListChangedListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MetadataProxy, SageMediaFileMetadataProxy, UserRecordMetadataProxy

    public abstract class AbstractMetadataProxy
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.reflect.InvocationHandler, IPropertyListChangedListener, ISageMetadata
    Abstract Proxy class for Metadata. If you are simply storing your metadata as strings then subclass this class and implement the required methods for setting/getting metadata from your structure.
